567fail:

622free_PKCS8EncryptedData(PKCS8EncryptedData *data)
623{
624der_free_octet_string(data);
625}

628length_PKCS8EncryptedData(const PKCS8EncryptedData *data)
629{
630size_t ret = 0;
631ret += der_length_octet_string(data);
632ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);

636int ASN1CALL
637copy_PKCS8EncryptedData(const PKCS8EncryptedData *from, PKCS8EncryptedData *to)
638{
639memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));

647int ASN1CALL
648encode_PKCS8EncryptedPrivateKeyInfo(unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, const PKCS8EncryptedPrivateKeyInfo *data, size_t *size)
649{
650size_t ret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = 0;
651size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
652int i HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
653
654/* encryptedData */
655{
656size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
657ret = 0;
658e = encode_PKCS8EncryptedData(p, len, &(data)->encryptedData, &l);
659if (e) return e;
660p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
661
662ret += Top_tag_oldret;
663}
664/* encryptionAlgorithm */
665{
666size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
667ret = 0;
668e = encode_AlgorithmIdentifier(p, len, &(data)->encryptionAlgorithm, &l);
669if (e) return e;
670p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
671
672ret += Top_tag_oldret;
673}
674e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, CONS, UT_Sequence, &l);
675if (e) return e;
676p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
677
678*size = ret;
679return 0;
680}
681
682int ASN1CALL
683decode_PKCS8EncryptedPrivateKeyInfo(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, PKCS8EncryptedPrivateKeyInfo *data, size_t *size)
684{
685size_t ret = 0;
686size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
687int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
688
689memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
690{
691size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
692Der_type Top_type;
693e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_Sequence, &Top_datalen, &l);
694if (e == 0 && Top_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
695if(e) goto fail;
696p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
697Top_oldlen = len;
698if (Top_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
699len = Top_datalen;
700e = decode_AlgorithmIdentifier(p, len, &(data)->encryptionAlgorithm, &l);
701if(e) goto fail;
702p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
703e = decode_PKCS8EncryptedData(p, len, &(data)->encryptedData, &l);
704if(e) goto fail;
705p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
706len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
707}
708if(size) *size = ret;
709return 0;
710fail:
711free_PKCS8EncryptedPrivateKeyInfo(data);
712return e;
713}
714
715void ASN1CALL
716free_PKCS8EncryptedPrivateKeyInfo(PKCS8EncryptedPrivateKeyInfo *data)
717{
718free_AlgorithmIdentifier(&(data)->encryptionAlgorithm);
719free_PKCS8EncryptedData(&(data)->encryptedData);
720}
721
722size_t ASN1CALL
723length_PKCS8EncryptedPrivateKeyInfo(const PKCS8EncryptedPrivateKeyInfo *data)
724{
725size_t ret = 0;
726{
727size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
728ret = 0;
729ret += length_AlgorithmIdentifier(&(data)->encryptionAlgorithm);
730ret += Top_tag_oldret;
731}
732{
733size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
734ret = 0;
735ret += length_PKCS8EncryptedData(&(data)->encryptedData);
736ret += Top_tag_oldret;
737}
738ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
739return ret;
740}
741
742int ASN1CALL
743copy_PKCS8EncryptedPrivateKeyInfo(const PKCS8EncryptedPrivateKeyInfo *from, PKCS8EncryptedPrivateKeyInfo *to)
744{
745memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
746if(copy_AlgorithmIdentifier(&(from)->encryptionAlgorithm, &(to)->encryptionAlgorithm)) goto fail;
747if(copy_PKCS8EncryptedData(&(from)->encryptedData, &(to)->encryptedData)) goto fail;
748return 0;
749fail:
750free_PKCS8EncryptedPrivateKeyInfo(to);
751return ENOMEM;
752}
